        The Scottish star of 300 and Gods of Egypt posted a photo of the remains of his Malibu home on Instagram on Sunday, thanking firefighters for their "courage". In addition to the photo, Butler also posted two videos on his Instagram stories, saying that his house is "half gone".
                
                
                
                
                
            
            
        Robin Thicke
                
                
                
                
                
                 Image copyright
                 Getty Images
                
            
            
        Robin Thicke's partner April Love Geary, who is currently pregnant, revealed on Instagram stories that their home had been destroyed.The previous day, the Blurred Lines singer posted photos of the smoke near their home in Malibu.
    
        
            Skip Instagram post  by aprillovegeary
